# Provider smoke: register a NullProvider; exercise its four
# protocol methods. Results are deterministic per Python ref's
# NullProvider semantics (zvfs.py:558-613): walk always yields
# NodeID 1 (NOTFOUND), stat returns dir for item 0 / notfound
# elsewhere, path returns the static [NULL] marker.
provider null
walk 0 nonexistent 0
stat 0 0
stat 0 5
path 0 0
